  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-wrap">
      <div class="cta-left fade-in">
        <span class="section-label">Open Challenge</span>
        <div class="section-divider"></div>
        <h2>Challenge Our Governance</h2>
        <p>Submit a governance scenario. We&rsquo;ll show you exactly how PureBrain handles it &mdash; what fires, what prevents it, and what happens if something slips through.</p>
